  "texts": [
    "The learning rate decay factor was set to 0.8 for these models.",
    "Training is stopped if a maximum number of epochs is reached, or the validation loss does not improve for a maximum number of early stopping patience.",
    "The ViSNet model trained on the molecular dynamic datasets and Molecule3D had 9 hidden layers and the embedding dimension was set to 256.",
    "We used a larger model for the QM9 dataset, i.e., the embedding dimension changed to 512.",
    "For the OGB-LSC PCQM4Mv2 dataset, we use the 12-layer and 768-dimension Transformer-M 37 as the backbone."
